data.description: Luxury townhome in gated community is close to pool, clubhouse, shopping and restaurants. A wide foyer leads to living area w/10 ft ceilings. Gorgeous open kitchen has granite on countertops and stainless steel appliances, including the refrigerator. Two separate dining areas are ideal for broadly entertaining or use either for more intimate gatherings. Go chill and grill on the covered patio, then relax in main level primary suite. There is plenty of room for an extensive wardrobe in the well appointed closet. An upper bonus room w/full bath and dual closets offers private space for guests or transform it to an incredible media space. Spacious laundry room plumbing already in for a utility sink. Loan is assumable to other VA eligible buyers.
